  <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEditRectangulo">
   <property name="geometry">
    <rect>
     <x>10</x>
     <y>40</y>
     <width>511</width>
     <height>361</height>
    </rect>
   </property>
   <property name="font">
    <font>
     <family>Segoe UI</family>
    </font>
   </property>
   <property name="cursor" stdset="0">
    <cursorShape>ArrowCursor</cursorShape>
   </property>
   <property name="styleSheet">
    <string notr="true">border: none</string>
   </property>
   <property name="readOnly">
    <bool>true</bool>
   </property>
   <property name="html">
    <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Segoe UI'; font-size:8.25pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Título:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt; Rectângulo&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Texto:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;O rectângulo é uma figura geométrica plana que possui quatro lados, sendo que os lados opostos são iguais e todos os ângulos internos são retos (90°). É uma das figuras mais comuns na geometria e aparece frequentemente em construções, cálculos de área e problemas de álgebra.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Área:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Calcula-se multiplicando a base pela altura do rectângulo:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;	&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;Á&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;rea = base * altura&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Perímetro:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;É a soma de todos os lados, ou duas vezes a soma da base com a altura:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;	&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;code-block-viewer&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;erímetro = 2 * (base + altura)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Propriedades importantes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Possui quatro ângulos retos (90°). &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Os lados opostos são paralelos e iguais. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;É um caso especial de paralelogramo. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Pode ser usado como base para calcular o perímetro e a área de outras figuras compostas. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt;O rectângulo é fundamental em geometria, engenharia, arquitetura e cálculos matemáticos, servindo como referência para muitas outras formas planas. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
   </property>
